TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Likelihood Approach to Pooling Cross-Section and Time-Series Data
AU  - Maddala, G. S.
AB  - [The paper discusses the problem of pooling cross-section and time-series data in the framework of likelihood functions and the associated posterior distributions and shows how this analysis can be useful in deciding whether or not to pool.]
